American developers, The Wenger’s, live in the Northern suburbs of Chicago, with their two daughters, Ashley and Jamie. Joshua graduated from Boston University, with a Bachelor of Science in Hospitality, and has over 19 years of management working in the food service industry. He is currently employed by Aramark as the Director of Food services in a school district, on the North Shore of Chicago. Robyn works in the Compliance Department for CVS/Caremark and has recently gone back to college, where she is studying Communications. \n\nJoshua and Robyn have been athletic all their lives and have instilled this into their two girls. They both love running; between half marathons and full marathons they can\'t get enough! Their love for running inspired them to create this app that will help people keep all their race history in once central location.
